Telkom in About Selling a 20% Stake to Korea Telecom, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-10-14T04:42:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/telkom-in-about-selling-a-20-stake-to-korea-telecom-business-day-reports.html
Telkom South Africa Ltd. is in talks
to sell a 20 percent stake to Korea Telecom in a deal that could
be worth as much as 4.6 billion rand, Business Day reported,
citing unidentified people close to the companies.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  